<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li class="font-semibold">Thay pin iPhone 13 ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng Pisen: 1.050.000&nbsp;₫</li>
<li class="font-semibold">Thay pin iPhone 13 Pro ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng Pisen: 1.190.000&nbsp;₫</li>
<li class="font-semibold">Thay pin iPhone 11 Pro Max ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng Vmas: 790.000&nbsp;₫</li>
